Who eventually conquered the Byzantine Empire?;The Muslim Turks
What year did the Byzantine Empire end?;1453
Who was the last Byzantine Emperor's niece who married Ivan III?;Sophia Paleologue
What did some Russians call their empire after Sophia Paleologue married Ivan III?;The Third Rome
